## Summary

This room covers the fundamentals of Incident Response — the structured process of handling cyber security incidents from start to finish. The practical exercise involved responding to a phishing email incident, identifying infected hosts, containing the threat, and eradicating the malware across multiple hosts in a network.

## Tools Used

- SIEM — log collection and correlation
- EDR — endpoint detection and response
- Playbooks — step-by-step IR guidelines

